================================================================================
A statistical approach for inferring the 3d structure of the Genome
================================================================================

"A statistical approach for inferring the three-dimensional structure of the
genome" N. Varoquaux, F. Ay, W. S. Noble and J.-P. Vert


COMPILATION
===============================================================================

1) First install IPOPT: https://projects.coin-or.org/Ipopt
IPOPT can be installed anywhere, you will have to tell "3dmodel" where IPOPT is.
2) The "3dmodel" directory can be anywhere you like. 
3) You have to edit the file Makefile, and set the following 3 variables at the
top: IPOPTPATH, IPOPTINCDIR, IPOPTLIBDIR.
4) Type make. 


RUNNING
===============================================================================
Run:
./genome_ipopt_main
without any arguments to get a help message. 
